title: BBS Driver's Test + Men's vs Women's Bathrooms + Clint Black In Studio
itunes:title: BBS Driver's Test + Men's vs Women's Bathrooms + Clint Black In Studio
description:
Mike D prepared a BBS Driver's Test for all the show members to take as part of a bet. The loser has to wash everyone's feet on tomorrow's show! Bobby draws attention to the many differences between men's and women's bathrooms. Plus, Clint Black stops by the studio to chat and perform!
